lesson_monitoring:explicit_lesson_standard('IM-G6-U7-L4', ccss, '4.NBT.A.2', "Read and write multi-digit whole numbers using base-ten numerals, number names, and expanded form. Compare two multi-digit numbers based on meanings of the digits in each place, using >, =, and < symbols to record the results of comparisons.").
